  "cta": "free-trial",
  "description": "5-step walkthrough: Sign in and download transcripts Follow this simple 5-step walkthrough to sign in and download your IRS transcripts. The screens shown are i",
  "content": "<div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; gap:24px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:18px;\">\n      <div style=\"max-width:720px;\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\">5-step walkthrough: Sign in and download transcripts</h1>\n        <p class=\"sub\" style=\"margin:0;\">Follow this simple 5-step walkthrough to sign in and download your IRS transcripts. The screens shown are instructional mockups to help you confidently navigate your IRS.gov account.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-start;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"btn primary tm-btn-regular\" style=\"text-decoration:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; white-space:nowrap;\">\n          Go to IRS.gov\n          <svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M7 17L17 7\" />\n            <path d=\"M7 7h10v10\" />\n          </svg>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"player\" aria-label=\"Walkthrough player\">\n      <div class=\"player-top\">\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"crumbs\" id=\"crumbs\">Step 1 of 5</div>\n          <div class=\"step-title\" id=\"stepTitle\">Loading…</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"controls\">\n          <button class=\"btn\" type=\"button\" id=\"btnPrev\">Prev</button>\n          <button class=\"btn primary\" type=\"button\" id=\"btnPlay\">Play</button>\n          <button class=\"btn\" type=\"button\" id=\"btnNext\">Next</button>\n          <button class=\"btn\" type=\"button\" id=\"btnReplay\">Replay</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"stage\" aria-label=\"Walkthrough stage\">\n        <!-- Step 1: ID.me-like sign-in (generic) -->\n        <section class=\"screen\" id=\"s0\" aria-label=\"Step 1 mock\">\n          <div class=\"frame\">\n            <div class=\"barTop\">\n              <div class=\"brand\"><span class=\"logo\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Identity Provider</div>\n              <div class=\"barDots\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\" style=\"display:grid; place-items:center;\">\n              <div class=\"card\" style=\"width:min(430px, 100%);\">\n                <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-size:16px;\">Sign in</h3>\n                <div class=\"muted\" style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">Authenticate with your identity provider to continue.</div>\n                <div class=\"rows\">\n                  <div class=\"row\"><span>Email</span><small>example@domain.com</small></div>\n                  <div class=\"row\"><span>Password</span><small>••••••••</small></div>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-top:12px;\">\n                  <span class=\"pill\">Remember me</span>\n                  <span class=\"cta\">Continue</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Step 2: Dashboard (generic) -->\n        <section class=\"screen\" id=\"s1\" aria-label=\"Step 2 mock\">\n          <div class=\"frame\">\n            <div class=\"navSim\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <span>Account Home</span>\n              <span>Account Balance</span>\n              <span>Payments</span>\n              <span class=\"active\">Records and Status</span>\n              <span>Notices</span>\n              <span>Forms</span>\n              <span>Authorizations</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\">\n              <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px;\">\n                <div>\n                  <div class=\"muted\" style=\"margin-bottom:6px;\">Account Home</div>\n                  <div style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:1000; letter-spacing:-.01em;\">Welcome, Taxpayer</div>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"pill\">Profile</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom:14px;\">\n                <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Unexpected outreach?</h3>\n                <div class=\"muted\">If something feels off, pause and verify through official channels.</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"grid2\">\n                <div class=\"rows\">\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Account Status</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Your most recent return status and processing updates.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:10px;\" class=\"row\"><span>Return status</span><small>Not processed</small></div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Payments</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Make a payment or review activity.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:10px;\" class=\"cta\">Make a payment</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"rows\">\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Notifications</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Important updates you may need to review.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:10px;\" class=\"row\"><span>Confirm mailing address</span><small>1 unread</small></div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Records and Status</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Tax records, transcripts, refund status, and more.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:10px;\" class=\"rows\">\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Tax Records</span><small>View filings</small></div>\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Transcripts</span><small>Download</small></div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Step 3: Records and Status menu open (generic) -->\n        <section class=\"screen\" id=\"s2\" aria-label=\"Step 3 mock\">\n          <div class=\"frame\">\n            <div class=\"navSim\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <span>Account Home</span>\n              <span>Account Balance</span>\n              <span>Payments</span>\n              <span class=\"active\">Records and Status</span>\n              <span>Notices</span>\n              <span>Forms</span>\n              <span>Authorizations</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menuOpen\" aria-label=\"Records and Status menu\">\n              <div><strong>Information Return Documents</strong><span>View available documents</span></div>\n              <div class=\"primary\"><strong>Tax Records</strong><span>View key tax info</span></div>\n              <div><strong>Audit Status</strong><span>Review audits</span></div>\n              <div><strong>Refund Status</strong><span>View status</span></div>\n              <div><strong>Amended Return Status</strong><span>View status</span></div>\n              <div><strong>Transcripts</strong><span>Download transcripts</span></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\">\n              <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Records and Status</h3>\n                <div class=\"muted\">Use this menu to get to Tax Records, then View transcripts.</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\n                <div class=\"muted\">This is a UI storyboard, not a functional portal.</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Step 4: Tax Records with View transcripts button (generic) -->\n        <section class=\"screen\" id=\"s3\" aria-label=\"Step 4 mock\">\n          <div class=\"frame\">\n            <div class=\"navSim\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <span>Account Home</span>\n              <span>Account Balance</span>\n              <span>Payments</span>\n              <span class=\"active\">Records and Status</span>\n              <span>Notices</span>\n              <span>Forms</span>\n              <span>Authorizations</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\">\n              <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:flex-end; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin-bottom:12px;\">\n                <div>\n                  <div class=\"muted\" style=\"margin-bottom:6px;\">Account Home / Tax Records</div>\n                  <div style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:1000; letter-spacing:-.01em;\">Tax Records</div>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"pill\">Select tax year</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"grid2\">\n                <div class=\"rows\">\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Return summary</h3>\n                    <div class=\"rows\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Tax year</span><small>2024</small></div>\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Form filed</span><small>1040</small></div>\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Filing status</span><small>Single</small></div>\n                      <div class=\"row\"><span>Adjusted gross income</span><small>$0.00</small></div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Clean vehicle credit information</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Expand the year to view credit details.</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"rows\">\n                  <div class=\"card\" id=\"viewTxCard\">\n                    <h3>Transcripts</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">View the most recent account, return, wage &amp; income, and record of account transcripts.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:12px;\" class=\"cta\" id=\"viewTxBtn\">View transcripts</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Tax compliance report</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">A report that summarizes compliance status.</div>\n                    <div style=\"margin-top:12px;\" class=\"cta\">Get report (PDF)</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Step 5: Transcripts page (generic) -->\n        <section class=\"screen\" id=\"s4\" aria-label=\"Step 5 mock\">\n          <div class=\"frame\">\n            <div class=\"navSim\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <span>Account Home</span>\n              <span>Account Balance</span>\n              <span>Payments</span>\n              <span class=\"active\">Records and Status</span>\n              <span>Notices</span>\n              <span>Forms</span>\n              <span>Authorizations</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"content\">\n              <div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">\n                <div class=\"muted\" style=\"margin-bottom:6px;\">Account Home / Tax Records / Transcripts</div>\n                <div style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:1000; letter-spacing:-.01em;\">Transcripts</div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom:14px;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px;\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Customer File Number</h3>\n                    <div class=\"muted\">Optional label for your records.</div>\n                  </div>\n                  <span class=\"pill\">Collapsed</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"txGrid\" aria-label=\"Transcript types\">\n                <div class=\"txCard\" id=\"txAccount\">\n                  <h4>Account transcripts</h4>\n                  <div class=\"muted\">Payments, penalties, adjustments, and account activity.</div>\n                  <div class=\"txList\">\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2024</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2023</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2022</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"txCard\" id=\"txReturn\">\n                  <h4>Return transcripts</h4>\n                  <div class=\"muted\">Most line items from your original return.</div>\n                  <div class=\"txList\">\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2024</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2023</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2022</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"txCard\" id=\"txWage\">\n                  <h4>Wage &amp; income transcripts</h4>\n                  <div class=\"muted\">W-2, 1099, and other information returns.</div>\n                  <div class=\"txList\">\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2025</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2024</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2023</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"txCard\" id=\"txRecord\">\n                  <h4>Record of account transcripts</h4>\n                  <div class=\"muted\">Combines return and account details.</div>\n                  <div class=\"txList\">\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2024</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                    <div class=\"txItem\"><span>2023</span><span class=\"txLinks\"><a href=\"#\">EN</a><a href=\"#\">ES</a></span></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"caption\">\n        <div class=\"timeline\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"bar\" id=\"bar\"></div></div>\n        <strong id=\"capStrong\">…</strong>\n        <span id=\"capSpan\">…</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"steps\" aria-label=\"Step selectors\">\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-step=\"0\"><b>1</b><span>Sign in</span></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-step=\"1\"><b>2</b><span>Dashboard</span></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-step=\"2\"><b>3</b><span>Records menu</span></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-step=\"3\"><b>4</b><span>View transcripts</span></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-step=\"4\"><b>5</b><span>Download EN/ES</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"note\">\n      <strong>Important:</strong> This page is an instructional demonstration designed to help you understand the transcript ordering process. The screens shown are simplified mockups for educational purposes and are not affiliated with or operated by the IRS.\n    </div>",
